sentence: Looking at options trading activity among components of the S&P 500 index, there is noteworthy activity today in Apache Corp (Symbol: APA), where a total volume of 37,881 contracts has been traded thus far today, a contract volume which is representative of approximately 3.8 million underlying shares (given that every 1 contract represents 100 underlying shares).
That number works out to 60.7% of APA's average daily trading volume over the past month, of 6.2 million shares.

Particularly high volume was seen for the $22.50 strike call option expiring November 15, 2019, with 12,566 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 1.3 million underlying shares of APA.
